==About==
Bog Brain is a common battle [[Bog Parasites|Bog-Parasite]].

Playing Bog Brain has no effect, except expending it and gaining experience with it.

==Hatch==
When Bog Brain Hatches, it's transformed into a random uncommon battle Bog Parasite, so [[Branch]], [[Delirium]] or [[Fever]].